Use the standard library
This is how to valid_date of date:
   Remember that s is date
   When isarray of date, then:
      Remember that s is ""
      Remember that n is date's length
      Remember that i is 0
      Do this n times:
         Add s to item i in date
         Increase i
      End do
   End when
   When s's length is not 10, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   When item 2 in s is not 45, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   When item 5 in s is not 45, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this 10 times:
      When i is not 2, then:
         When i is not 5, then:
            Remember that c is item i in s
            When c is less than 48, then:
               The answer is 0
            End when
            When c is more than 57, then:
               The answer is 0
            End when
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   Remember that month_s is ""
   Add month_s to item 0 in s
   Add month_s to item 1 in s
   Remember that day_s is ""
   Add day_s to item 3 in s
   Add day_s to item 4 in s
   Remember that year_s is ""
   Add year_s to item 6 in s
   Add year_s to item 7 in s
   Add year_s to item 8 in s
   Add year_s to item 9 in s
   Remember that month is toint of month_s
   Remember that day is toint of day_s
   Remember that year is toint of year_s
   When month is less than 1, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   When month is more than 12, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   Remember that maxday is 31
   When month is 4, then:
      Remember that maxday is 30
   End when
   When month is 6, then:
      Remember that maxday is 30
   End when
   When month is 9, then:
      Remember that maxday is 30
   End when
   When month is 11, then:
      Remember that maxday is 30
   End when
   When month is 2, then:
      Remember that maxday is 28
      When leap_year of year, then:
         Remember that maxday is 29
      End when
   End when
   When day is less than 1, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   When day is more than maxday, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   The answer is 1
